@startuml Trip Management Sequence Diagram (Detailed)

title Trip Management Sequence Diagram (By Page & Service)

actor ":Staff" as Staff
actor ":Renter" as Renter
participant ":StaffBookingDetailPage" as SBD
participant ":RenterBookingPage" as RBP
participant ":SuccessPage" as SP
participant ":BookingService" as BS
participant ":PaymentTransactionService" as PTS
participant ":PayosService" as PS
participant ":Payment Gateway" as PAYOS

note across
  **Precondition:** Booking is **CONFIRMED**.
  Deposit paid, cars assigned.
  Continues from Booking Sequence Diagram.
end note

' ── 1. Staff Views Booking ──
Staff -> SBD : 1. View booking (CONFIRMED)
activate SBD
SBD -> BS : 1.1 getAdminBookingById(bookingId)
activate BS
BS --> SBD : 1.2 AdminBookingResponse
deactivate BS
SBD --> Staff : 1.3 Display booking detail page
deactivate SBD

' ── 2. Staff Confirms Pickup ──
Staff -> SBD : 2. Click "Confirm Pickup"
activate SBD
SBD -> BS : 2.1 confirmPickup(bookingId)
activate BS
note right of BS
  Validate status == CONFIRMED.
  Set actualReceiveDate = now().
  CONFIRMED → **IN_PROGRESS**.
end note
BS --> SBD : 2.2 AdminBookingResponse (IN_PROGRESS)
deactivate BS
SBD --> Staff : 2.3 Success notification
deactivate SBD

' ── GPS Tracking ──
note over SBD
  **GPS Tracking (client-side emulation)**
  Leaflet.js + OpenStreetMap.
  Simulated car movement every 3s.
  No backend calls.
end note

' ── 3. Staff Confirms Return ──
Staff -> SBD : 3. Click "Confirm Return"
activate SBD
SBD -> BS : 3.1 confirmReturn(bookingId)
activate BS
note right of BS
  Validate status == IN_PROGRESS.
  Set actualReturnDate = now().
  Compare actual vs expected return.
end note

alt On time or early
    BS -> BS : 3.2a Set status → COMPLETED
    BS --> SBD : 3.3a AdminBookingResponse (COMPLETED)
    deactivate BS
    SBD --> Staff : 3.4a "Booking Complete" banner
    deactivate SBD

else Late return — overdue
    note right of BS
      Calculate overdue charge:
      ceil(overdueHours) × hourlyRate × 1.5.
      Update totalPrice & remainingAmount.
      Keep status = IN_PROGRESS.
    end note
    BS -> PTS : 3.2b createPayment(bookingId,\nOVERDUE_PAYMENT, overdueCharge)
    activate PTS
    PTS -> PAYOS : 3.3b createPaymentLink(orderCode, amount)
    activate PAYOS
    PAYOS --> PTS : 3.4b checkoutUrl
    deactivate PAYOS
    PTS --> BS : 3.5b PaymentTransactionResponse
    deactivate PTS
    BS --> SBD : 3.6b AdminBookingResponse\n(IN_PROGRESS, overdueCharge)
    deactivate BS
    SBD --> Staff : 3.7b Overdue alert + pending payment
    deactivate SBD

    ' ── 4. Renter Pays Overdue ──
    Renter -> RBP : 4. View booking, click "Pay Now"
    activate RBP
    RBP -> PAYOS : 4.1 Redirect to payment checkout
    deactivate RBP

    Renter -> PAYOS : 5. Complete overdue payment
    activate PAYOS
    PAYOS -> PS : 5.1 handleWebhook(orderCode, PAID)
    activate PS
    note right of PS
      OVERDUE_PAYMENT → PAID.
      All payments resolved →
      IN_PROGRESS → **COMPLETED**.
    end note
    deactivate PS
    PAYOS --> SP : 5.2 Redirect to success page
    deactivate PAYOS
    activate SP
    SP --> Renter : 5.3 Payment success
    deactivate SP
end

' ── 6. Booking Complete ──
Staff -> SBD : 6. View booking
activate SBD
SBD -> BS : 6.1 getAdminBookingById(bookingId)
activate BS
BS --> SBD : 6.2 AdminBookingResponse (COMPLETED)
deactivate BS
SBD --> Staff : 6.3 "Booking Complete" (no further actions)
deactivate SBD

Renter -> RBP : 7. View booking
activate RBP
RBP -> BS : 7.1 getBookingById(bookingId)
activate BS
BS --> RBP : 7.2 BookingResponse (COMPLETED)
deactivate BS
RBP --> Renter : 7.3 Booking completed, all payments resolved
deactivate RBP

note across
  **Final Status: COMPLETED.**
  All payments settled. Booking lifecycle ends.
end note

@enduml
